<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Payment" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Payment,</orth> 1) the act of paying, of giving in compensation: <cit><quote>reward not hospitality with such black p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 576" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 576</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the p. of a hundred thousand crowns,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 2.130" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL II, 130</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lll 2.130" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL II, 130</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.186" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 186</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.32" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 2.2.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. II, 2, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.4.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 4, 161</bibl>.<lb />2) that which is given in compensation: <cit><quote>fair p. for foul words,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.1.19" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 1, 19</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>too little p. for so great a debt,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 5.2.154" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. V, 2, 154</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tn 4.1.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. IV, 1, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.5.135" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 5, 135</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.174" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 1, 174</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 5.1.116" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. V, 1, 116</bibl>.
<lb />3) requital: <cit><quote>if he come to-morrow, I'll give him his p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.166" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 166</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.15" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 8, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.4.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 4, 19</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>